# 🚀 AE's Notebook – Sprint Plan (Replit)

This sprint plan outlines the phased development of the AE's Notebook using Replit, Supabase, and GitHub. Each sprint is 1 week long.

---

## 🏁 Sprint 0: Environment Setup & Planning

### 🎯 Goal:
Set up the Replit environment, version control, and authentication backend.

### ✅ Tasks:
- [ ] Create a new Replit workspace for AE's Notebook.
- [ ] Connect project to GitHub repo.
- [ ] Initialize Supabase project.
- [ ] Design database schema (users, notebooks, days, tasks, notes, etc).
- [ ] Install Supabase client SDK and test basic auth.
- [ ] Create basic folder structure for components and services.

---

## 🚧 Sprint 1: MVP Core Features

### 🎯 Goal:
Build the core layout, authentication, and basic notebook functionality.

### ✅ Tasks:
- [ ] Implement login, sign up, guest access, and password reset (Supabase auth).
- [ ] Build sidebar with ability to:
  - [ ] Add, rename, delete notebooks (except default)
  - [ ] Add quarters, weeks, and auto-generated days
- [ ] Auto-select current date or create it on load
- [ ] Create pages for each view: Notebook View, Meeting Notes View
- [ ] Quota Overview section:
  - [ ] Add/Edit/Delete categories
  - [ ] Press "Enter" to add new categories
  - [ ] Collapsible quota section with hidden totals when collapsed
- [ ] Weekly Target Accounts list:
  - [ ] Add by typing and pressing enter
  - [ ] Add sub-tasks with checkboxes using Tab
- [ ] Morning Tasks / To-Do Lists:
  - [ ] Each day starts blank (no carry-over)
  - [ ] Add checkable tasks with sub-tasks
  - [ ] Rich text formatting toolbar
- [ ] Save all user input to Supabase by account

---

## 🧠 Sprint 2: Notes, UX Polish, and Export

### 🎯 Goal:
Complete meeting notes, improve UI, and build export tools.

### ✅ Tasks:
- [ ] Meeting Notes View:
  - [ ] Notes auto-assign to current date
  - [ ] Allow reassignment to a different day
  - [ ] Upload/paste images into notes
  - [ ] Copy button copies title, date, text, and category
- [ ] Ensure sidebar remains visible across views
- [ ] Add collapsible Weekly Target + Morning Tasks/To-Do sections side-by-side
- [ ] Ensure Tab key creates sub-task checkbox lines
- [ ] Match behavior across light and dark mode
- [ ] Add export button to email/copy notes
- [ ] Ensure responsive layout on mobile and desktop

---

## 🔮 Sprint 3: Optional (AI Assistant & Team Sharing)

### 🎯 Goal:
Add smart assistant and prepare for user collaboration and paid features.

### ✅ Tasks:
- [ ] Build AI Assistant:
  - [ ] Embed GPT chatbot trained on user's data (notes, tasks, quotas)
  - [ ] Enable queries like “What’s my biggest priority today?”
- [ ] Create team-sharing (if scoped in)
- [ ] Add user settings and basic plan info
- [ ] Stripe integration (for future billing)
- [ ] Final performance tuning

---

## 📦 Deployment Tasks (across sprints)

- [ ] Connect to GitHub for version control
- [ ] Deploy to Netlify or Vercel
- [ ] Set up environment variables for Supabase keys
- [ ] Test login persistence across devices
- [ ] Share live link with collaborators

---

